<template><ModulePageShell title="PACU专项" description="基于OperationCase与真实PACU结构化记录"><template #chips><a-tag color="arcoblue">PACU记录 {{rows.length}}</a-tag><a-tag color="orangered">未转出 {{inRoom}}</a-tag></template><template #toolbar><a-button :loading="loading" @click="reload">刷新</a-button></template><a-alert v-if="error" type="error" show-icon>{{error}}</a-alert><a-empty v-else-if="!loading&&!rows.length" description="当前病例范围无PACU记录"/><a-card v-else class="section-card" :bordered="false" title="PACU质控病例"><a-table :data="rows" row-key="operationId" :pagination="{pageSize:10}"><a-table-column title="患者" data-index="patientName"/><a-table-column title="手术" data-index="operationName"/><a-table-column title="入室" data-index="admittedAt"/><a-table-column title="转出" data-index="dischargedAt"/><a-table-column title="恢复评分" data-index="recoveryScore"/><a-table-column title="状态" data-index="status"/><a-table-column title="操作"><template #cell="{record}"><a-link @click="router.push(`/pacu/record/${record.operationId}`)">恢复记录</a-link></template></a-table-column></a-table></a-card></ModulePageShell></template>
<script setup lang="ts">import{computed,onMounted,ref}from'vue';import{useRouter}from'vue-router';import ModulePageShell from'@/components/shared/ModulePageShell.vue';import{qualityApi}from'@/api/quality';interface Row{operationId:string;patientName:string;operationName:string;admittedAt:string|null;dischargedAt:string|null;recoveryScore:number|null;status:string}const router=useRouter(),rows=ref<Row[]>([]),loading=ref(false),error=ref('');const inRoom=computed(()=>rows.value.filter(x=>!['discharged','transferred','已转出'].includes(x.status)).length);async function reload(){loading.value=true;error.value='';try{const r=await qualityApi.caseList({page:1,pageSize:100});rows.value=(r.items??r.list).flatMap(x=>{const p=x.moduleSummaries?.pacu as Record<string,unknown>|null|undefined;if(!p)return[];return[{operationId:x.operationId,patientName:String(x.operationCase.patientName??''),operationName:String(x.operationCase.operationName??''),admittedAt:p.admittedAt?String(p.admittedAt):null,dischargedAt:p.dischargedAt?String(p.dischargedAt):null,recoveryScore:p.recoveryScore==null?null:Number(p.recoveryScore),status:String(p.status??'')}];});}catch(e){rows.value=[];error.value=`加载失败：${(e as Error).message}`;}finally{loading.value=false;}}onMounted(reload);</script>
